children.text: The correct size reinforcement specified by the engineer has not been installed, and the replacement is not of equivalent strength.
The relevant Australian Standard, AS 2870 Residential Slabs and Footings states in section 3.7 Reinforcement Equivalences that
‘The bar sizes given in Table 3.3 are deemed to comply with the requirements for trench mesh reinforcement in beams and footings’.
The laps to these bars will need to be rectified prior to any concrete being poured.
